    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>West African chordophones consisting of a stick or narrow board and a tall notched bridge over which the strings pass in a vertical alignment.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
